Last 2 Walk is the 9th album from Memphis rap group Three 6 Mafia. The album was set to be released December 4, 2007, but has been pushed back to June 24, 2008.
The album was pushed back several times, originally scheduled for release May 6 2007 , but has been pushed back several times until finally was set for June 24, 2008. The album was named Last 2 Walk because DJ Paul and Juicy J are the last two 
members remaining in Three 6 Mafia. Three 6 Mafia originally started with six core members.

Guest features on the album include Project Pat, Lil Wyte, Akon, Good Charlotte, DJ Unk, Lyfe Jennings, UGK, Eightball & MJG, Al Kapone, DJ Spanish Fly, Frayser Boy, Yung D, Superpower.
